<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="15">Culture characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="15">Culture incubated on PNA at 25 °C, originally white, fluffy aerial mycelium, reverse yellowish pigmentation developing in centre, later becoming dark brown, with yellowish-cream drops exuding from the perithecia after 15 days.</paragraph>
